@token = 
############################################
### 1. 크리에이터 오퍼 목록 조회  (creator_id = 1)
###  → users.json + campaign_acceptance.json에 따르면
###    creator 1은 acceptance pk = 1(1), 3(2), 8(7), 11(9) 세 개 존재
############################################
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/creator/6/offers/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


############################################
### 2. 캠페인 수락 테스트 (creator 1 → campaign 1 or 3)
### campaign_acceptance.json  확인 결과:
### creator 1 은 campaign_id 1, 7, 9(accepted), campaign_id 2(rejected)
### → campaign 1,7,9 수락 테스트
############################################
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/creator/6/campaign/1/accept/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json



############################################
### 3. 캠페인 거절 테스트 (creator 6 → campaign_id 2)
############################################
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/creator/6/campaign/2/reject/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json


############################################
### 4. 진행 상황 조회 (deliverables)  (creator_id = 6)
### deliverable.json 확인 결과:
### campaign_id 1, 7 -> completed, campaign_id 9-> incomplete
############################################
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/creator/6/progress/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


############################################
### 5. 포스팅 업로드 테스트 (creator 1 → accepted campaign_id 1)
############################################
